# 🧮 1781. Sum of Beauty of All Substrings

🔗https://leetcode.com/problems/sum-of-beauty-of-all-substrings/description/

## ✅ Approach:
-Maintaining prefix sum in every iteration of i loop,
every iteration of j loop is a substring and for every substring k loop calculates the beauty sum

## ⏱️ Time Complexity:
- Time - O(N^2)*26 --> O(N^2)
- Space - O(1)


## 🔤 Code (Java):
```java
class Solution {
    public int beautySum(String s) {
        int N=s.length();
        int sum=0;
        for(int i=0;i<N;i++){
            int[] arr=new int[26];
            for(int j=i;j<N;j++){

                char c=s.charAt(j);
                arr[c-'a']+=1;
                int min=N;
                int max=0;
                for(int freq:arr){
                    if(freq>0){
                        min=Math.min(min,freq);
                        max=Math.max(max,freq);
                    }
                }
               sum+=(max-min);

            }
            
        }
        return sum;
    }
}
